{"tid":2357646,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★Twitter警告Trump：帳號將被永久停用！","createTime":"2021-01-07T14:22:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T14:33:12.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"241571b52b03d00bf8eb07e1fdd87ced28f21835","tid":2357646,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T14:22:39.000Z","msg":"美國國會昨日（6 日）起進行確認大選各州選舉人投票結果程序的聯席會議，有總統特朗普的支持者到國會示威，控訴選舉不公，而特朗普亦在同日上載在白宮前發表演說的影片，並呼籲示威者回家，惟 Twitter、Facebook 以及 YouTube 均移除予相關演說片段，並指將會暫時停止特朗普的帳號使用權。<br />\n<br />\n 美國國會在昨日（6 日）舉行聯席會議，認證大選的選舉人票結果，有總統特朗普的支持者到國會示威，以控訴選舉不公。特朗普同日在其 Twitter 及 Facebook 帳號上載其在國會開會前夕，於白宮外舉行「拯救美國」（Save America）集會的演說，重申大選不公，揚言自己不會放棄和承認落敗，並呼籲示威者回家。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n然而，Twitter 在同日以特朗普的帖文多次嚴重違反公司的《公民誠信政策》（Civic Integrity Policy）為由，刪除特朗普帳戶較早時發出的帖文，同時宣布封鎖總統特朗普的帳戶 12 小時，並警告若其再違規，帳號將有可能被<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>永久停用</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2021/01/07/trump-social-media/life-tech/social-network/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2021%2F01%2F07%2Ftrump-social-media%2Flife-tech%2Fsocial-network%2F&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z7BzIjlmttHRdZ2xAWa028c%3D&h=4d77250f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2021/01/07/trump-social-media/life-tech/social-network/</a>"},{"pid":"188642f90af59f3ebd76ab3ec80d137ff3dde95f","tid":2357646,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T14:22:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f833f7bb71e7f26b86d6d0483909fde20c66f104","tid":2357646,"uid":5737,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T14:23: